438
00:34:31,943 --> 00:34:33,296
<i>Soy la misma persona.</i>

439
00:34:34,103 --> 00:34:35,822
<i>Tengo que pensar. Me voy.</i>

440
00:34:37,183 --> 00:34:38,094
